#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:1 of
msgid "Access a group of rows and columns by label(s) or a boolean array."
msgstr "通过标签或布尔数组访问一组行和列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:3 of
msgid ""
"``.loc[]`` is primarily label based, but may also be used with a boolean "
"array."
msgstr "``.loc[]`` 主要基于标签，但也可以与布尔数组一起使用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:6 of
msgid "Allowed inputs are:"
msgstr "允许的输入包括："

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:8 of
msgid ""
"A single label, e.g. ``5`` or ``'a'``, (note that ``5`` is interpreted as"
" a *label* of the index, and **never** as an integer position along the "
"index)."
msgstr ""
"单个标签，例如 ``5`` 或 ``'a'``，（注意 ``5`` 被解释为索引的 *标签*，而 *"
"*不是** 索引上的整数位置）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:11 of
msgid "A list or array of labels, e.g. ``['a', 'b', 'c']``."
msgstr "标签列表或数组，例如 ``['a', 'b', 'c']``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:12 of
msgid "A slice object with labels, e.g. ``'a':'f'``."
msgstr "一个带有标签的切片对象，例如 ``'a':'f'``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:14 of
msgid ""
"Note that contrary to usual python slices, **both** the start and the "
"stop are included"
msgstr "请注意，与常规的 Python 切片不同，起始和结束位置都包含在内。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:17 of
msgid ""
"A boolean array of the same length as the axis being sliced, e.g. "
"``[True, False, True]``."
msgstr "与被切片轴长度相同的布尔数组，例如 ``[True, False, True]``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:19 of
msgid ""
"An alignable boolean Series. The index of the key will be aligned before "
"masking."
msgstr "可对齐的布尔 Series。在进行掩码操作前，键的索引将被对齐。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:21 of
msgid "An alignable Index. The Index of the returned selection will be the input."
msgstr "可对齐的 Index。返回的选择的 Index 将是输入本身。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:22 of
msgid ""
"A ``callable`` function with one argument (the calling Series or "
"DataFrame) and that returns valid output for indexing (one of the above)"
msgstr ""
"一个接受一个参数（调用的 Series 或 DataFrame）并返回有效索引输出（以上"
"之一）的 ``callable`` 函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:25 of
msgid "See more at :ref:`Selection by Label <indexing.label>`."
msgstr "更多信息请参见 :ref:`通过标签选择 <indexing.label>`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:27 of
msgid "If any items are not found."
msgstr "如果找不到任何项目。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:28 of
msgid ""
"If an indexed key is passed and its index is unalignable to the frame "
"index."
msgstr "如果传递了一个带索引的键，但其索引无法与框架索引对齐。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.at`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:33 of
msgid "Access a single value for a row/column label pair."
msgstr "访问一个行/列标签对的单个值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.iloc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:36 of
msgid "Access group of rows and columns by integer position(s)."
msgstr "通过整数位置访问行和列的组。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:38 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.xs`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:39 of
msgid "Returns a cross-section (row(s) or column(s)) from the Series/DataFrame."
msgstr "从 Series/DataFrame 返回一个横截面（行或列）。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:41 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.loc`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:42 of
msgid "Access group of values using labels."
msgstr "使用标签访问值的组。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:45 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:46 of
msgid "**Getting values**"
msgstr "**获取值**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:58 of
msgid "Single label. Note this returns the row as a Series."
msgstr "单个标签。请注意这将返回一行作为 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:65 of
msgid "List of labels. Note using ``[[]]`` returns a DataFrame."
msgstr "标签列表。请注意使用 ``[[]]`` 将返回一个 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:72 of
msgid "Single label for row and column"
msgstr "行和列的单个标签"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:77 of
msgid ""
"Slice with labels for row and single label for column. As mentioned "
"above, note that both the start and stop of the slice are included."
msgstr ""
"使用标签切片行和单个标签切片列。如上所述，请注意切片的起始和结束都包含"
"在内。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:85 of
msgid "Boolean list with the same length as the row axis"
msgstr "与行轴长度相同的布尔列表"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:91 of
msgid "Alignable boolean Series:"
msgstr "可对齐的布尔 Series："

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:98 of
msgid "Index (same behavior as ``df.reindex``)"
msgstr "索引（行为与 ``df.reindex`` 相同）"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:106 of
msgid "Conditional that returns a boolean Series"
msgstr "返回布尔 Series 的条件表达式"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:112 of
msgid "Conditional that returns a boolean Series with column labels specified"
msgstr "返回指定列标签的布尔 Series 的条件表达式"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:118 of
msgid "Callable that returns a boolean Series"
msgstr "返回布尔 Series 的可调用对象"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:124 of
msgid "**Setting values**"
msgstr "**设置值**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:126 of
msgid "Set value for all items matching the list of labels"
msgstr "为匹配标签列表的所有项设置值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:135 of
msgid "Set value for an entire row"
msgstr "为整行设置值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:144 of
msgid "Set value for an entire column"
msgstr "为整列设置值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:153 of
msgid "Set value for rows matching callable condition"
msgstr "为满足可调用条件的行设置值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:162 of
msgid "**Getting values on a DataFrame with an index that has integer labels**"
msgstr "**在具有整数标签索引的 DataFrame 上获取值**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:164 of
msgid "Another example using integers for the index"
msgstr "另一个使用整数作为索引的示例"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:174 of
msgid ""
"Slice with integer labels for rows. As mentioned above, note that both "
"the start and stop of the slice are included."
msgstr "使用整数标签切片行。如上所述，请注意切片的起始和结束都包含在内。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:183 of
msgid "**Getting values with a MultiIndex**"
msgstr "**使用 MultiIndex 获取值**"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:185 of
msgid "A number of examples using a DataFrame with a MultiIndex"
msgstr "使用具有 MultiIndex 的 DataFrame 的多个示例"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:205 of
msgid "Single label. Note this returns a DataFrame with a single index."
msgstr "单个标签。请注意这将返回一个具有单个索引的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:212 of
msgid "Single index tuple. Note this returns a Series."
msgstr "单个索引元组。请注意这将返回一个 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:219 of
msgid ""
"Single label for row and column. Similar to passing in a tuple, this "
"returns a Series."
msgstr "行和列的单个标签。类似于传入一个元组，这将返回一个 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:227 of
msgid "Single tuple. Note using ``[[]]`` returns a DataFrame."
msgstr "单个元组。请注意使用 ``[[]]`` 将返回一个 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:233 of
msgid "Single tuple for the index with a single label for the column"
msgstr "索引的单个元组与列的单个标签"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:238 of
msgid "Slice from index tuple to single label"
msgstr "从索引元组切片到单个标签"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.loc:249 of
msgid "Slice from index tuple to index tuple"
msgstr "从索引元组切片到索引元组"

